		  <td width="135" class="forum_boardrow2" style="border-width: 0px 0px 1px 1px;" valign="top"><div id="messageuser27634541" style="padding-bottom: 2px;"><a href="/profile/Gonzo-nyan"><strong>Gonzo-nyan</strong></a></div>
		  
		  <a href="/profile/Gonzo-nyan"><img src="http://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/useravatars/985071.jpg" vspace="2" border="0"></a>
		  <br>
		  Offline<br>
