		  <td class="forum_boardrow1" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 1px;" valign="top"><div id="message27667203">Koyomi Araragi<br />
<br />
I've grown astoundingly fond of this well developed MC. And the 2013 Second Series only developed him further, giving him lots of in-universe room to grow as he came to terms with some very difficult situations, including losing some very close friends. He became much more self-reliant in SS, handling dangerous and dire situations on his own (or just with the help of his shadow) where before he needed Meme Oshino's help for even the smallest incidents. As a character that we've gotten to watch grow and develop into a harem-toting, spirit-fighting, romantic, deep petitioner of justice, Araragi is my choice for MC of the Year.</div><div class="postActions"></div><div class="sig"><span style="font-size: 80%;"><div style="text-align: center;"><img class="userimg" data-src="http://fc06.deviantart.net/fs42/f/2009/096/7/8/Tonberry_Banner_by_Doaj.jpg" /><br />
